title: latlongformat
---
type: filter
---
signature: value, secs=True
---
summary: Formats the latitude and longitude into a string
---
body:

This formats a latitude and longitude tuple into a human readable string
in the format degrees, minutes and seconds.  See also [latformat
:ref](../latformat/) and [longformat :ref](../longformat/).

## Examples

```html+jinja
<p>Location: {{ image.exif.location|latlongformat }}
```
